<reference id="enum_agoramediaplayerrendermodetype">
    <title><ph keyref="AgoraMediaPlayerRenderMode"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">Video display modes.</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title>Enumerator</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><ph keyref="AgoraMediaPlayerRenderModeHidden"/></pt>
                    <pd>1: Uniformly scale the video until one of its dimension fits the boundary
                        (zoomed to fit). Hidden mode. One dimension of the video may have clipped
                        contents.</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><ph keyref="AgoraMediaPlayerRenderModeFit"/></pt>
                    <pd>2: Uniformly scale the video until one of its dimension fits the boundary
                        (zoomed to fit). Fit mode. Areas that are not filled due to disparity in the
                        aspect ratio are filled with black.</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
